Japan May Pass Energy, Deficit Bills by Aug. 26, Kyodo Says

-- B y   G o   O n o m i t s u
-- 
2011-08-10T02:24:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-10/japan-may-pass-energy-deficit-bills-by-aug-26-kyodo-says.html
Japan ’s ruling and opposition
parties will aim to pass a renewable-energy bill and a deficit-
covering bond bill by Aug. 26,  Kyodo News  reported.  The chairmen of the parliamentary-affairs committees of the
 Democratic Party  of Japan and the  Liberal Democratic Party   made
the agreement today, according to the report, which didn’t say
where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Go Onomitsu in Tokyo at 
